// Man page for binary
manBinary="BINARY(1)                        X Shell Manual                        BINARY(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    bin - Binary to decimal converter
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>bin BINARY</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Convert binary numbers to decimal format.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>bin 11111111</b>
    Convert binary to decimal (255)

    <b>bin 101010</b>
    Convert binary to decimal (42)

    <b>bin 1000</b>
    Convert binary to decimal (8)
<b>SEE ALSO</b>
    <b>decimal</b>"